The Biggest Loser Australia - Families Season 10 Episode 02

Hosted by Fiona Falkiner, this season of TBL Families will see the trainers each paired with one Aussie family of four, as they motivate them to achieve their weight-loss dreams.

An emotional weigh-in sees the contestants step on the scales to reveal the true extent of their unhealthy habits. Later, the four families finally meet each other at their first team challenge
